  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392540/extras/38a8b71ed4e7479a5e8ff75293e0a171.webp?t=1604654365\" width=600 height=52 /></span><br><br>      《缄默星空》是一款飞船驾驶的冒险游戏。你将扮演星际佣兵布莱特，在艾叶西利亚星域进行一场惊心动魄的冒险故事，谱写一首传奇的太空史诗。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392540/extras/c7670df758ce5065ebb475a0f3922e46.webp?t=1604654365\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392540/extras/d4ae9100c9248dd19f1743982efd5d56.webp?t=1604654365\" width=600 height=52 /></span><br><br>      玩家所扮演的星际佣兵布莱特，是一位接受了来自地方政府的委托，前往艾叶西利亚星域调查海盗暴动一事的传奇战士……怀有追寻失落神器踪迹这一秘密目的的他，在这里遭遇了一系列意外，逐渐与艾叶西利亚三位神女的命运纠葛在了一起，并发现了自己的身世由来以及独裁势力意图掀起战争、重建宇宙秩序的惊天密谋。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392540/extras/c7670df758ce5065ebb475a0f3922e46.webp?t=1604654365\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392540/extras/c4a705e4751afc620c397e993d629118.webp?t=1604654365\" width=600 height=52 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392540/extras/281e856d102a742790bcfdc13b23a3fc.webp?t=1604654365\" width=600 height=33 /></span><br>      游戏中共三十多个风格迥异、玩法各异的关卡，玩家需要利用关卡所带来的不同任务以及环境建立自己的优势。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392540/extras/cc0c81d6d8a112b314c63d18b1f9bb03.poster.avif?t=1604654365\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392540/extras/cc0c81d6d8a112b314c63d18b1f9bb03.webm?t=1604654365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392540/extras/cc0c81d6d8a112b314c63d18b1f9bb03.mp4?t=1604654365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392540/extras/5a24bb60fb7784ec52ba095c5a11fd21.webp?t=1604654365\" width=600 height=33 /></span><br>      游戏中玩家需要根据飞船的特性、装备的配置以及天赋的选择来搭配出玩家喜好的战斗玩法。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392540/extras/998a48a6a29e90caae19bf77aed3fb7b.poster.avif?t=1604654365\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392540/extras/998a48a6a29e90caae19bf77aed3fb7b.webm?t=1604654365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392540/extras/998a48a6a29e90caae19bf77aed3fb7b.mp4?t=1604654365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392540/extras/d78d509f7c13705a244dd3bef290839a.webp?t=1604654365\" width=600 height=33 /></span><br>      游戏通过多线故事交错叙事，玩家在做出不同选择时会对最终的结局带来决然不同的结果。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392540/extras/7ddcdfd526b86ae367267d463449aa34.poster.avif?t=1604654365\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392540/extras/7ddcdfd526b86ae367267d463449aa34.webm?t=1604654365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392540/extras/7ddcdfd526b86ae367267d463449aa34.mp4?t=1604654365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
